114 Section 4. Section 22-10B-7, Code of Alabama 1975,
115 relating to the Alabama Sickle Cell Oversight and Regulatory
116 Commission, is repealed.
117 Section 5. The Legislature concurs in the
118 recommendations of the Sunset Committee as provided in
119 Sections 1, 2, 3, and 4.
120 Section 6. This act shall become effective immediately.
